CHARITY DUPONT PORTFOLIO APP FOR iOS

This is a Progressive Web App (PWA). To install on your iPhone:

1. Open this website in Safari on your iPhone
2. Tap the Share button (square with arrow)
3. Scroll down and tap "Add to Home Screen"
4. Tap "Add" in the top right corner

The app will appear on your home screen with the portfolio icon.

For questions, contact: hello@charitydupont.com
